Subject: StealthAUDIT AIC error
Description: When searching for a user in AIC< an error is displayed.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Search user in AIC and try reports
What_We_Know__c:
Error message when trying to search user and view reports:
Sorry we are unable to complete this request right now, the application log file may contain helpful troubleshooting information.

url: /v2/admins/data/audit/reports/trustee/memberof
status: 500

It was believed that this issue was fixed in 11.6 so we upgraded from 11.5, but the issue persists
Next_Steps__c:
Fix is available in latest AIC build (v11.6.0.36). Customer said they will update ASAP and report back to us.

Customer OOO for the last 6 weeks, setting ticket to PPR 4/10 to give him some time to catch up.
Solution_Comment__c: Fix is available in latest AIC build (v11.6.0.36)
